media:group.media:title: This Amazing Cycling Bridge is Temporary #shorts #infrastructure
media:group.media:description:
The A9 Highway through Amstelveen is being widended and improved, with several sections being covered. While construction is underway, several temporary bicycle bridges were built to keep cycling safe and convenient until the project completes in 2026.
